description: This file is an architecture-specific include file for ARMv6 configurations within a Yocto Project build environment. It defines tuning parameters, compiler flags, package architectures, and features for ARMv6 in both little-endian and big-endian formats, with specific settings for various ARMv6 variants.

methods.name: bb.utils.contains
methods.description: Utility method used to check if a given feature is present in a list or string within the Yocto BitBake environment.
